      }, {
        "text": " Rate Scheduling:** Instead of a fixed learning rate, use a scheduler that reduces the rate when performance plateaus. This is crucial"
      }, {
        "text": " for fine-tuning in later epochs. Add `callbacks.ReduceLROnPlateau` to your `model.fit"
      }, {
        "text": "` call.\n\n**Action:**\nRun a 50-epoch training with a learning rate scheduler. This is our"
