        "text": "Target: 95-98%)\n\nOur current CNN is tiny. The paper\u0027s \"simple\" CNN"
      }, {
        "text": " was likely more substantial.\n\n1.  **Add Batch Normalization:** Add a `layers.BatchNormalization()` layer"
      }, {
        "text": " after each `Conv2D` and `QAConv24` layer (before the activation). This dramatically stabilizes training and often"
      }, {
        "text": " improves accuracy.\n2.  **Go Deeper:** Add another convolutional block (e.g., `Conv2D(2"
      }, {
        "text": "56, ...)` -\u003e `BatchNormalization` -\u003e `Activation` -\u003e `MaxPool2D`). Deeper models can"
      }, {
        "text": " learn more complex features.\n3.  **Integrate QA Features at the Head:** The QA signatures are powerful."
      }, {
